A fixed-price currency where bitcoins can be bought and sold.  This is a cash exchange and not an online service.

The rates are based on the current BTC/USD market rate from [[MtGox]].  The minimum transaction size is R$ 200,00 (duzentos reais).

Currencies traded for bitcoins include BRL (Brazilian Real) and USD.  Bitcoins may be sold for either currency as well.

##History

The service was announced on March 31st, 2011 (2.1).

